I21Based on title 5, U.S.C., 1946 ed., ÿ1A41, and on title 14, U.S.C., 1946 ed. ÿ1A22, 58, 91, 99, 103 (R.S. 2749; June 18, 1878, ch. 265, ÿ1A7, 8, 22 Stat. 164; May 4, 1882, ch. 117, ÿ1A5, 22 Stat. 57; Mar. 4, 1907, ch. 2918, 34 Stat. 1309; Jan. 28, 1915, ch. 20, ÿ1A1, 38 Stat. 800; Aug. 29, 1916, ch. 417, 39 Stat. 601; June 10, 1921, ch. 18, ÿ1A304, 42 Stat. 23; July 3, 1926, ch. 742, ÿ1A9, 44 Stat. 817).

